Achieve the same frequency and resonance between university spirit and time spirit - Xinhuanet The so-called university spirit refers to a series of theories on school management and value pursuit formed by a university after long-term accumulation during development, which is the spirit of a university. The university spirit is critical to the development of politics, economics, culture, science and technology and society or even progress of a nation in all ages. Colleges and universities have undertaken unique mission different from other social organizations since the establishment of the first university of the modern significance; for universities and colleges in our country, they emerged during the time of stress of our country, with the spirit deeply influenced by traditional culture and time changes; the value idea of “benefitting the mankind and assisting in nation governance” and the patriotism of “developing the country through education” was advocated. At present, with increasingly prominent trend of information and internationality in higher education, there are increasingly fierce education competition, science and technology competition and talent competition all over the whole world; as the important “supply end”, the structural reform of higher education is facing with unprecedented opportunities and challenges. Especially, the proposal of the General Scheme for Promoting the Construction of the Global Top Universities and the Top Subjects shows the confidence and determination of our country in developing to a giant of higher education from a big country of higher education, which proposes higher and newer requirements on development of universities. How to rank among the best in the world with a short time, to construct global top universities and global top subjects in the condition of some differences, to realize “corner overtaking”? In addition to insisting on objective confidence, path confidence and ability confidence, universities and colleges shall also give full play to three advantages: the first one is the late-mover advantage: realizing significant improvement on academic level and school operation quality by introducing overseas excellent academic talents and learning advanced experience from global top universities; the second one is the cultural advantage: inheriting the wisdom of the Chinese civilization accumulated for five thousand years and developing excellent traditional culture, to unify strength, build brand and improve image; the third one is the system advantage: give play to the superiority of the system in the socialist country, strengthening objective driving, collecting consensus and resultant force, optimizing resource configuration, and providing sustainable and solid guarantee for the school to catch up with and surpass the world advanced standard. It shall be realized that in order to construct global top universities, universities shall manifest individualities and characteristics at the same time of bringing superiority into full play. The school operation characteristics shall reflect the common Chinese characteristics and manifest unique objective location, school operation traditions and resource endowment. With respect to Zhejiang University, features on three aspects are emphasized in school operation: the first one is to highlight the features of innovation and entrepreneurship talent training: constructing integrated teaching environment by combining science with education and combining schools and enterprises, to form the full-chain entrepreneurship education ecological system; the second one is to highlight the feature of crossed subjects: promoting optimized adjustment of subject system, building the environment of the crossed-subject system, and actively training the crossed emerging subjects and the landmark crossed achievements; the third one is to highlight the school operation system and the social service features: developing deep international exchange and cooperation and accelerating forming the industry-university-research cooperation system of Zhejiang University. During this process, the most important thing is insisting on the university spirit, to achieve the same frequency and resonance between university spirit and time spirit. As for Zhejiang University, the school motto of “truth and innovation”, the common value system of “diligence, morality, discrimination and honesty” as well as “inclusiveness, reality, morality, practice and country governance” constitute the latest expression system of the spirit of Zhejiang University. This is the school operation direction and the important guarantee for cultural accumulation and mental strength, with abundant connotation and profound significance. In which, “inclusiveness” emphasizes the spirit of inclusiveness, reflecting the mind of “inviting all talents”, expressed as adopting the good idea of school operation and talent training in world famous schools; “reality and morality” lays emphasis on the spirit of pursuit for truth and kindheartedness, meaning that universities shall pay attention to morality at the same time of pursuing for truth; “practice” reflects the spirit of reform and innovation, including innovation in knowledge and science and technology, expressed as reform, development and innovation; “country governance” lays emphasis on the spirit of love the country and contribution, saying that universities shall always share the glory and disgrace with the destiny of the country. The series of spiritual idea and value pursuit is the spirit of Zhejiang University with the history of 120 years. “Clever people can hear speechless voices and wisdom people can see invisible things”. It is necessary for universities and colleges in China to further master the time direction and the historical mission of higher education based on the overall situation of the socialism with Chinese characteristics, to accelerate to become world top universities. At the same time, stick to humanistic care, independence and freedom, to make university spirit, time spirit and national spirit promote each other, so as to provide power for realizing state prosperity, national rejuvenation and common ideal of human.
